Heat the tomato in the sink and take it out.

high_descs: Go straight down this hall, then take the left to the kitchen area, walking to the microwave in the corner to the right.
Remove the knife from the microwave.
Walk along the counters to get to the sink in the same area.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Look to the counters next to the sink.
Place the knife down on the counter.
Look back to the sink with the sliced tomato.
Pick up one tomato slice.
Go back to the microwave you got the knife from.
Use the microwave on the tomato slice and pick it back up.
Look to the counter the microwave is sitting on.
Place the tomato slice in front of the microwave.
